1OL.F.summary: Odd Molly International AB (publ) designs, markets, and sells fashion and other lifestyle products for girls and woman under the Odd Molly brand name worldwide. The company offers short and long dresses; sweaters, cashmere, cardigans, canna cardigans, and lovely knits; blouses, T-shirt/tops, and tanks; pants, skirts, jeans, and leggings; jackets and coats, and skiwear; and lingerie and accessories, as well as home dÃ©cor products. The company sells its products through its own sales channels and retailers. It operates through 16 own stores in Sweden, Norway, and Finland; and 7 partner-run stores in the United States, the Czech Republic, Slovakia, and Portugal, as well as a Web shop. The company was founded in 2002 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.

HM-B.ST.short_name: Hennes & Mauritz AB, H & M ser.
HM-B.ST.summary: H & M Hennes & Mauritz AB (publ) provides clothing, accessories, footwear, cosmetics, home textiles, and homeware for women, men, teenagers, children, and babies worldwide. It offers sportswear, shoes, bags, beauty products, stationery, and ready-to-wear; and interior products, including bed linens, dinnerware, textiles, furniture, and lamps. The company provides its products under the H&M, H&M HOME, COS, & Other Stories, Monki, Weekday, ARKET, Afound, and Sellpy brands. As of September 30, 2020, the company had 51 online markets and approximately 5,000 stores in 74 markets, including franchise markets. H & M Hennes & Mauritz AB (publ) was founded in 1947 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.

NIL-B.ST.summary: NilÃ¶rngruppen AB produces and sells labels, packaging products, and accessories primarily in the fashion and garment industries in Nordic countries, rest of Europe, and Asia. It offers various woven, textile, and embossed labels, as well as hang tags; and packaging products, such as labelled boxes, cartons, and paper and plastic bags. The company also provides accessories, including buttons, zip pulls, buckles, silicones, leather products, etc.; and garment care labels. In addition, it offers security and anti-counterfeit products, as well as solutions for variable data/RIS applications. The company was founded in 1970 and is headquartered in Boras, Sweden.
